Getting started
===============

    $ cd src
    $ autoconf
    $ make

     - src/tests-sbox      : test codes
          /sbox.{c,h}      : system call hooks
          /strace.c        : main

    $ ./strace -h          : help
    $ ./strace ls          : give it a shot
    $ ./testall.sh         : test all unit tests
    
    $ ./strace -s ls       : run ls with seccomp/bpf (if supported)

Use cases
=========

    $ ./strace -i -- wget google.com      : a simple use
    $ ./strace -n -i -- wget google.com   : no network
